Cristiano Ronaldo scored his 300th goal for Real Madrid against Rayo Vallecano on April 8 . 
  The Portuguese forward reached the landmark in only his 288th game for the club . 
  Real Madrid president Florentino Perez presented Ronaldo with a special shirt with '300 goals' on the back . 
  Ronaldo only trails Raul and Alfredo di Stefano in the scoring charts . 
  Karim Benzema will miss Real Madrid's clash with Malaga on Saturday . 
 